                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>Additional details about goods, works and services inspected are enlisted in the attached Certificate of
Inspection and Acceptance (ref: 27849).
In view of a forgoing; the committee recommends payment processing to the supplier/contractor against goods, works and services accepted as per the terms and conditions of the contract.</Value>
                    <Style>
