                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>We the undersigned, being members of the IAC confirm that we have performed the assignment and issued this Inspection and Acceptance Report and certificate of inspection and acceptance for the herein above enlisted goods, wörks and services, having accepted them:</Value>
