                    <Value>Kindly note that, in addition to any other that may be required from time to time, all payments to suppliers/contractors will be supported by following documents: (i) Inspection and Acceptance Committee's Report; (ii) Certificate of Inspection and Acceptance; (iii) Delivery Note; (iv) Invoice; and (v) LPO/Contract.</Value>
